org.apache.hadoop.hbase.client

接口 AsyncRegistry

  • 所有超级接口:
    AutoCloseable, Closeable
    所有已知实现类:
    ZKAsyncRegistry

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
interface AsyncRegistry
extends Closeable
    Implementations hold cluster information such as this cluster's id, location of hbase:meta, etc.. All stuffs that may be related to zookeeper at client side are placed here.

    Internal use only.
